<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-10-0728 </DOCNO><TEXT>An effective polarizer for thermal and epithermal neutrons is possiblewith polarized, high density, gaseous /sup 3/He. We describe the techniqueof /sup 3/He polarization by spin exchange with laser optically pumpedRb vapor which can provide 6 cm/sup 3/ of andgt; 70% polarized /sup 3/He ata density of 3x10/sup 20/ atoms cm/sup -3/ (10 atm at STP). The /sup3/He polarization can be rapidly reversed, a requirement for sensitivesymmetry tests.</TEXT></DOC>